datas.title: Can I resell an NFT?
datas.content: What you do own when you buy an NFT are the keys to a non-fungible – perhaps unique – token. That token is yours to trade or hold or display in Decentraland. But the digital file associated with an NFT is just as easy to copy and paste and download as any other – the Finally, players lose their NFTs sometimes according to the rules and regulations of the NFT game.
